{"lemma":"طِيبَةُ","slug":"طِيبَةُ","root":"ط.#.ب","root_slug":"ط-_-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-_-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"طِيبَةُ","root":"طيب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":30},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27403","n27411","n27412","n27418"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"feminine singular of طَيِّب (ṭayyib)","tags":["feminine","form-of","singular"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"singular of طَيِّبَات (ṭayyibāt)","tags":["form-of","singular"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/tˤaj.ji.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27403","headword_ar":"طيّبهُ","root":"Tyb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, MA, O, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taToyiybN","text_ar":"تَطْيِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (KL;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ATAbhu","text_ar":"اطابهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAbahu","text_ar":"طَابَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (IAar, M, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, made it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered it, good, pleasant, delightful, delicious, sweet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"savoury: perfumed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered fragrant, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, MA, O, * K, * KL:) [and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made it"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered it, pure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clean:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see 1, first sentence:)] you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ty~b julasaA='ahu","text_ar":"طيّب جُلَسَا=ءَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He perfumed his companions with whom he was sitting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ty~b Alv~awoba","text_ar":"طيّب الثَّوْبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAbahu","text_ar":"طَابَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He perfumed the garment"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (IAar, M, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~abotuhu","text_ar":"طَيَّبْتُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I daubed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smeared, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, with perfume,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"some odoriferous"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fragrant substance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~abahu biAlT~iybi","text_ar":"طَيَّبَهُ بِالطِّيبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He perfumed him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"daubed him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smeared him, with some odoriferous"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fragrant substance"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ty~b binafosihi","text_ar":"طيّب بِنَفْسِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ty~b nafosahu","text_ar":"طيّب نَفْسَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which latter is a phrase of frequent occurrence, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He placated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soothed, his mind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he spoke to him pleasantly, sweetly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blandly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~abota nafosiY Eanoka","text_ar":"طَيَّبْتَ نَفْسِى عَنْكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou hast made me to be pleased,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"happy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"content, without thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"slw","text_ar":"سلو"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ty~bhu","text_ar":"طيّبهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made it lawful, allowable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"free."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, from a trad.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~aba ligariymihi niSofa AlmaAli","text_ar":"طَيَّبَ لِغَرِيمِهِ نِصْفَ المَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He acquitted his debtor of the half of the property; gave up, resigned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remitted, it to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b4-  See also 10."}],"source_refs":["S","M","A","MA","O","Msb","K","IAar","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n27411","headword_ar":"طَيْبَةُ","root":"Tyb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"a name of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The city of the Prophet;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAbapu","text_ar":"طَابَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~ay~ibapu","text_ar":"الطَّيِّبَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmuTay~abapu","text_ar":"المُطَيَّبَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which last may be also written ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmuTay~ibapu","text_ar":"المُطَيِّبَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n27412","headword_ar":"طِيبَةٌ","root":"Tyb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAba","text_ar":"طَابَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O, K.) ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clearest"},{"kind":"text","text":"of wine: (K:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"choicest"},{"kind":"text","text":"of herbage. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tiybapu","text_ar":"طِيبَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a name of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The well Zemzem."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]},{"entry_id":"n27418","headword_ar":"طَيِّبَةٌ","root":"Tyb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~ibN","text_ar":"طَيِّبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and also a subst., made so by the affix"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A good, pleasant, delightful, delicious, sweet"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"savoury, thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clean, thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~ibaAtN","text_ar":"طَيِّبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA@lT~ay~ibaAti mina","text_ar":"وَا@لطَّيِّبَاتِ مِنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~izqi","text_ar":"الرِّزقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [vii. 30], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And what are esteemed"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasant, delicious, sweet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"savoury, of foods and beverages."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anofiquwA mino Tay~ibaAti maA kasabotumo","text_ar":"اَنْفِقُوا مِنْ طَيِّبَاتِ مَا كَسَبْتُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the same [ii. 269],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Expend ye of the good things that ye have gained:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of your lawful gains."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuluwA mina A@lT~ay~ibaAti","text_ar":"كُلُوا مِنَ ا@لطَّيِّبَاتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the same [xxiii. 53], (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Eat ye of the things that are lawful; of any such lawful things as are esteemed good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~ay~ibaAtu mina AlkalaAmi","text_ar":"الطَّيِّبَاتُ مِنَ الكَلَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The most excellent of words,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speech;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the best thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and is meant by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~ay~ibaAtu","text_ar":"الطَّيِّبَاتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in [the words of] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta$ah~ud","text_ar":"تَشَهُّد"},{"kind":"text","text":", [commencing with]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aHiy~aAtu lil~`hi waAlS~alawaAtu waAlT~ay~ibaAtu","text_ar":"التَّحِيَّاتُ لِلّٰهِ وَالصَّلَوَاتُ وَالطَّيِّبَاتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHiy~apN","text_ar":"تَحِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HY","text_ar":"حى"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and likewise in the Kur [xxiv. 26], where it is said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~ay~ibaAtu lilT~ay~ibiyna","text_ar":"الطَّيِّبَاتُ لِلطَّيِّبِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; by the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ty~byn","text_ar":"طيّبين"},{"kind":"text","text":"being meant"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the pure of men;"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to Fr.: but these words of the Kur are otherwise expl., as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the good women are for the good men."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tayobapu","text_ar":"طَيْبَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}